       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DISPLAY-RESULTS.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  IDX     PIC 9 VALUE 1.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  D-SCORES.
           05  D-SCORE OCCURS 3 TIMES PIC 9(3).
       01  D-AVERAGE PIC 9(3)V9(2).


       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING D-SCORES, D-AVERAGE.
       DISP-RESULT-PARA.
           DISPLAY "SCORES ENTERED: "
           PERFORM VARYING IDX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL IDX > 3
               DISPLAY "Score " IDX ": " D-SCORE(IDX)
           END-PERFORM

           DISPLAY "Average Score: " D-AVERAGE
           EXIT PROGRAM.
